{"tid":880296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★「香港年金計劃」市傳有一成的長者突然「抽飛」","createTime":"2018-10-28T15:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T15:07:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5594f7c736557e5ca71dce8382217ff2a0e3c5bc","tid":880296,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"專為長者自製長糧、俗稱公共年金的「香港年金計劃」，市傳當分配結果出爐後，竟有約有一成的長者突然決定「抽飛」。<br />\n<br />\n香港年金公司發言人回覆《東網》指，現時銀行正陸續安排客戶投保，大部分已聯絡的客戶均有應約，料銀行需要多數星期時間才大致完成投保會面。<br />\n<br />\n至於實際投保人數，發言人稱在首批銷售程序完成後，將整理好相關資料並公布投保結果，亦會計劃和公布未來銷售及推廣計劃，包括考慮是否以持續銷售模式繼續營運香港年金計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181028/bkn-20181028185621366-1028_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181028%2Fbkn-20181028185621366-1028_00842_001.html&d=Yg98%2FVHvlNU702fI5xvPGgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=1787c135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181028/bkn-20181028185621366-1028_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a7150c7e7c8cb5a0fa234e19c9f81ecc0ffbf46","tid":880296,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f19d01e892f9ec0b3cec6ed0a7976ac023fb5e0","tid":880296,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi